## Integration / End-to-End

| Reference point | Status |
|---|---|
| Cross-component data flow — state written at one component visible at the next | Proposed |
| Transactional consistency — multi-step operations all-succeed or roll back cleanly | Proposed |
| Session / auth continuity — identity preserved across component boundaries | Proposed |

